{
  "uid": "aidra-orbital-resilience",
  "title": "AIDRA — Orbital Resilience",
  "description": "Resilience evidence: bit-flip degradation, autonomous decisions, drift detection, orbit battery simulation. All panels query PostgreSQL (resilience_runs / drift_alerts / orbit_sim_runs) so the dashboard survives Prometheus counter resets between deploys.",
  "tags": ["aidra", "orbital", "resilience", "bitflip", "autonomy"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "liveNow": false,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 2,
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30d",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {
    "refresh_intervals": ["10s", "30s", "1m", "5m"]
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "model_variant",
        "type": "query",
        "label": "Model Variant",
        "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
        "query": "SELECT DISTINCT model_variant FROM bitflip_runs ORDER BY model_variant",
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": "%",
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": "$__all" },
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1,
        "multi": false
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "title": "How to read this dashboard",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Orbital resilience** quantifies how AIDRA behaves under spaceflight constraints: cosmic-ray bit-flips on model weights, finite battery during eclipse, drift across long missions, and autonomous fallback decisions when energy is scarce.\n\nPopulate this dashboard by triggering the simulators (each call writes a row to PostgreSQL):\n\n```bash\n# Bit-flip sweep\ncurl -X POST $AIDRA_API/api/orbital/resilience/bitflip \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN' \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"vesseltracker-sar-yolov8\",\"flip_counts\":[0,10,100,1000]}'\n\n# Orbit simulation (small_sat / cubesat_3u / cubesat_6u / medium_sat)\ncurl -X POST $AIDRA_API/api/orbital/resilience/simulate-orbit \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN' \\\n  -d '{\"satellite\":\"small_sat\",\"num_images\":30}'\n\n# Drift check (no body, persists every call)\ncurl $AIDRA_API/api/orbital/resilience/drift?window_size=10 \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN'\n```"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Bit-Flip Degradation (max in window)",
      "description": "Maximum detection-degradation percentage observed under simulated bit-flips (SEU). Higher = more brittle.",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 8, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT COALESCE(MAX(degradation_pct) * 100, 0) AS max_degradation\nFROM bitflip_runs\nWHERE created_at BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()\n  AND model_variant LIKE '$model_variant'",
          "format": "table",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 10 },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 20 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 50 }
            ]
          },
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "noValue": "No bit-flip runs in window"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "showThresholdLabels": true,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true,
        "orientation": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Battery Level (last sim)",
      "description": "Final battery level (Wh) at the end of the most recent orbit simulation. Coloured by remaining capacity vs. nominal 100 Wh.",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": { "x": 8, "y": 4, "w": 8, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT final_battery_wh\nFROM orbit_sim_runs\nORDER BY created_at DESC\nLIMIT 1",
          "format": "table",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 20 },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 40 },
              { "color": "green", "value": 60 }
            ]
          },
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "unit": "watth",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "noValue": "No orbit simulations recorded"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "showThresholdLabels": true,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true,
        "orientation": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Decision Action Counters",
      "description": "Cumulative count of autonomous decisions across all orbit simulations: process (full inference), fallback_cfar (cheap detector), skip.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 16, "y": 4, "w": 8, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT\n  COALESCE(SUM(process_count), 0)        AS process,\n  COALESCE(SUM(fallback_cfar_count), 0)  AS fallback_cfar,\n  COALESCE(SUM(skip_count), 0)           AS skip\nFROM orbit_sim_runs\nWHERE created_at BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()",
          "format": "table",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "blue", "value": null }]
          },
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "noValue": "0"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "process" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "green", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "fallback_cfar" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "yellow", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "skip" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "orientation": "horizontal"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Bit-Flip Degradation Curve (detections vs num_flips)",
      "description": "Average detections per (model_variant, num_flips) cell across all bit-flip sweeps in the window. The X axis is num_flips (cosmic-ray-event proxy); a sharp drop identifies the model's critical SEU threshold.",
      "type": "barchart",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 10, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT\n  num_flips::text AS num_flips,\n  AVG(avg_detections) AS avg_detections,\n  AVG(avg_confidence) AS avg_confidence\nFROM bitflip_runs\nWHERE created_at BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()\n  AND model_variant LIKE '$model_variant'\nGROUP BY num_flips\nORDER BY num_flips::int",
          "format": "table",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 80,
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "axisCenteredZero": false
          },
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "noValue": "No bit-flip sweeps in window — POST /api/orbital/resilience/bitflip"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "avg_confidence" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "unit", "value": "percentunit" }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "orientation": "vertical",
        "barWidth": 0.7,
        "groupWidth": 0.7,
        "stacking": "none",
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": [] },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" },
        "xField": "num_flips",
        "showValue": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Battery Timeline (most recent orbit sim)",
      "description": "Battery level (Wh) at each decision step of the most recent simulated orbit. Drops mark eclipse / heavy inference; recoveries mark sun-lit recharge windows.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 10, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "WITH latest AS (\n  SELECT id, created_at, battery_timeline\n  FROM orbit_sim_runs\n  ORDER BY created_at DESC\n  LIMIT 1\n)\nSELECT\n  latest.created_at + (ord || ' minute')::interval AS time,\n  battery_wh\nFROM latest, unnest(latest.battery_timeline) WITH ORDINALITY AS t(battery_wh, ord)\nORDER BY ord",
          "format": "time_series",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "area" }
          },
          "color": { "mode": "continuous-GrYlRd" },
          "unit": "watth",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 20 },
              { "color": "green", "value": 50 }
            ]
          },
          "min": 0,
          "noValue": "No orbit simulations recorded — POST /api/orbital/resilience/simulate-orbit"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Drift Detection Alerts (per-day, by metric)",
      "description": "Daily count of drift checks that flagged a drifting metric. Bars are stacked by which signal drifted (detections / confidence / spatial).",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 18, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT\n  date_trunc('day', created_at) AS time,\n  metric,\n  COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE is_drifting) AS drifting_alerts\nFROM drift_alerts\nWHERE created_at BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()\nGROUP BY 1, 2\nORDER BY 1",
          "format": "time_series",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 80,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal" }
          },
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "noValue": "No drift checks recorded — GET /api/orbital/resilience/drift"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "num_detections" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "avg_confidence" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "orange", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "spatial" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "purple", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Autonomous Decision Mix Over Time",
      "description": "Per-day counts of autonomous decisions across simulations.  process = full inference; fallback_cfar = lightweight detector; skip = save energy.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 18, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT\n  date_trunc('day', created_at) AS time,\n  SUM(process_count)        AS process,\n  SUM(fallback_cfar_count)  AS fallback_cfar,\n  SUM(skip_count)           AS skip\nFROM orbit_sim_runs\nWHERE created_at BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()\nGROUP BY 1\nORDER BY 1",
          "format": "time_series",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal" }
          },
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "noValue": "No orbit simulations recorded"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "process" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "green", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "fallback_cfar" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "yellow", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "skip" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "Drift Check Log (recent)",
      "description": "Most recent drift checks: which metric was tested, the z-score against historical baseline, and the recommended action when drift was flagged.",
      "type": "table",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 24, "w": 24, "h": 7 },
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "PostgreSQL" },
          "rawSql": "SELECT\n  created_at         AS \"When\",\n  metric             AS \"Metric\",\n  is_drifting        AS \"Drifting\",\n  ROUND(z_score::numeric, 2)         AS \"Z-score\",\n  ROUND(recent_mean::numeric, 1)     AS \"Recent\",\n  ROUND(historical_mean::numeric, 1) AS \"Baseline\",\n  recommendation     AS \"Recommended\",\n  window_size        AS \"Window\"\nFROM drift_alerts\nWHERE created_at BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()\nORDER BY created_at DESC\nLIMIT 50",
          "format": "table",
          "editorMode": "code"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "align": "left", "filterable": true },
          "noValue": "No drift checks recorded"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Drifting" },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  { "type": "value", "options": { "true":  { "text": "yes", "color": "red" } } },
                  { "type": "value", "options": { "false": { "text": "no",  "color": "green" } } }
                ]
              },
              { "id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": { "type": "color-text" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "footer": { "show": false },
        "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "When", "desc": true }]
      }
    }
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  }
}
